desc: CHUBBY BUMS Brunei's First Adjustable Cloth Diaper READY, SET, BABY! Awareness and Educational Content for Parents, Guardians and Caretakers in Babies

layout.text: Here at Chubby Phat Kisses, we believe in quality products that are kind to our children and our planet. All our products are inspired by our baby girl, Giselle. Our promise to you is that we will only produce items that we are happy to use on Giselle. We hope our products will help enlighten your parenting journey by making a positive environmental impact one product at a time.
